    "en": {
      "title": "Three-hour power cut approved for tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) today approved a power cut of three hours for tomorrow (21).",
        "Accordingly, areas under group A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, P, Q, R, S, T, U, V and W will have one hour and 40 minutes during the daytime and one hour and 20 minutes during night.",
        "Meanwhile, areas under the group CC will experience a 2\u00bd hour\u00a0 powercut from 6.00 am to 8.30 am tomorrow.",
        "The areas listed under M, N, O, X, Y and Z group will experience a three hour powercut from 5.30 am to 8.30 am tomorrow. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
